data.chText: 创业者，企业家（尤指涉及财务风险的）
data.enText: a person who makes money by starting or running businesses, especially when this involves taking financial risks

simple_means.memory_skill: enterprise 企业；事业 + eur 人，物 → 企业家

means: 创业者(尤指涉及财务风险的)

tr: someone who organizes a business venture and assumes the risk for it

value.def: An entrepreneur is a person who sets up businesses and business deals.
